# @VERSION spec:gdla v:0.1.0 generated:2026-02-18 source:manual
# Sample GDLA fixture exercising all record types

@D petstore-api|Pet store management API|3.0.1|https://api.petstore.io/v1

@AUTH api_key|API key authentication|X-API-Key
@AUTH bearer|JWT bearer token|Authorization
@AUTH oauth2|OAuth 2.0 implicit flow|Authorization

@S Pet|A pet in the store
 id|integer|required|int64|Unique pet identifier
 name|string|required||Pet display name
 status|string||enum|Pet status in the store
 tags|Tag[]|||Optional classification tags
 category|Category|||Pet category

@S Tag|A tag for categorizing pets
 id|integer|required|int64|Tag identifier
 name|string|||Tag display name

@S Category|A pet category
 id|integer|required|int64|Category identifier
 name|string|||Category display name

@S Order|A store order
 id|integer|required|int64|Order identifier
 petId|integer|required|int64|Pet being ordered
 quantity|integer|||Number of pets
 shipDate|string||date-time|Expected ship date
 status|string||enum|Order status
 complete|boolean|||Whether order is complete

@S User|A registered user
 id|integer|required|int64|User identifier
 username|string|required||Login username
 email|string||email|User email address

@S Error|Standard error response
 code|integer|required|int32|HTTP status code
 message|string|required||Error description

@ENUM PetStatus|available,pending,sold
@ENUM OrderStatus|placed,approved,delivered

@EP GET /pets|List all pets|200:Pet[],400:Error|api_key
@P limit|query|integer||Maximum number of items to return
@P offset|query|integer||Number of items to skip
@P status|query|string||Filter by status

@EP POST /pets|Create a new pet|201:Pet,400:Error|bearer
@P body|body|Pet|required|Pet to create

@EP GET /pets/{petId}|Get pet by ID|200:Pet,404:Error|api_key
@P petId|path|string|required|The pet identifier

@EP PUT /pets/{petId}|Update a pet|200:Pet,400:Error,404:Error|bearer
@P petId|path|string|required|The pet identifier
@P body|body|Pet|required|Updated pet data

@EP DELETE /pets/{petId}|Delete a pet|204:,404:Error|bearer
@P petId|path|string|required|The pet identifier

@EP POST /pets/{petId}/uploadImage|Upload pet image|200:ApiResponse|bearer
@P petId|path|string|required|The pet identifier
@P file|body|binary|required|Image file to upload

@EP GET /store/inventory|Get inventory counts|200:object|api_key

@EP POST /store/orders|Place an order|201:Order,400:Error|bearer
@P body|body|Order|required|Order to place

@EP GET /users/{username}|Get user by username|200:User,404:Error|
@P username|path|string|required|Username to look up

# Escaped pipe in description
@EP GET /pets/search|Search pets with filters \| pagination|200:Pet[],400:Error|api_key
@P q|query|string|required|Search query

@EP PATCH /pets/{petId}|Partial update a pet|200:Pet,404:Error|bearer
@P petId|path|string|required|The pet identifier

@EP HEAD /pets|Check pets collection exists|200:|
@EP OPTIONS /pets|CORS preflight for pets|204:|

# GraphQL operations
@EP QUERY pets|Fetch pet list via GraphQL|200:Pet[]|bearer
@P limit|query|integer||Maximum items
@EP MUTATION createPet|Create a pet via GraphQL|200:Pet|bearer
@P input|body|Pet|required|Pet input data
@EP SUBSCRIPTION petUpdates|Subscribe to pet changes|200:Pet|bearer

@R Pet -> Tag|references|via tags
@R Pet -> Category|references|via category
@R Order -> Pet|references|via petId

@PATH User -> Order -> Pet|via /users/{id}/orders/{orderId}/pet
@PATH Store -> Inventory -> Pet|via /store/inventory -> /pets/{petId}
